    dc:creator "Marin, Ivan" ;
    dc:date "2009" ;
    dc:title "Crinoid-associated shrimps of the genus Laomenes A. H. Clark, 1919 (Caridea: Palaemonidae: Pontoniinae): new species and probable diversity" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185051>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185049>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185048>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185050>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185052> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185051>
    dc:description "FIGURE 33. Coloration of Laomenes ceratophthalmus (Borradaile, 1915) (A, C, E) and Laomenes nudirostris (Bruce, 1978) (B, D, F). A – D, ovigerous females. E, F, males." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185051/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185049>
    dc:description "FIGURE 31. Laomenes nudirostris (Bruce, 1978), ovigerous female (A – I), juvenile (J, K). A, B, J, K, distal part of carapace and rostrum. C, D, eyes. E, antenna. F, distal margin of incisor process. G, epistomial horns. H, thoratic sternite V with basal segments of pereiopod III. I, telson. Scale 1 mm; F, without scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185049/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185048>
    dc:description "FIGURE 30. Laomenes nudirostris (Bruce, 1978), ovigerous female. Scale 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185048/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185050>
    dc:description "FIGURE 32. Laomenes nudirostris (Bruce, 1978), ovigerous female (A – H), male (I). A, chela of pereiopod I. B, pereiopod II. C, D, same, carpus. E, same, finger. F, G, carpo-propodal articulation of pereiopod III. H, dactylus of pereiopod III. I, appendix masculina and appendix interna Scale 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185050/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185052>
    dc:description "FIGURE 34. Crinoid hosts of the representatives of the genus Laomenes A. H. Clark. A, Himerometra robustipinna (Carpenter, 1881) (Himerometridae). B, Amphimetra tesselata (Müller, 1841) (Himerometridae). C, Oxycomanthus benetti (Müller, 1841) (Comasteridae). D, F, Comantheria (Comanthus) briareus (Bell, 1882) (Comasteridae). E, Zygometra punctata A. H. Clark, 1912 (Zygometridae)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185052/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

